Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大海!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,的前夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,興致高漲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,花名 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看表情好像是有心事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不會游泳所以害怕海?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的 小花名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在海邊相互追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在沙灘寫下「love」然後讓海浪沖刷掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 但是 不是這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要穿比基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,想到要露出肚臍就緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,多露出點反而顯得身材好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說的話全裸不就是最強了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,露出肚臍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 現在就睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,明早還要早起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,去到了海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可以在榮依子你的身體上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,倒滿白色的滑溜溜的液體然後塗個遍可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好
